4Geeks Academy offers a comprehensive Data Science & Machine Learning course designed for beginners, aiming to start students on a career in data science within 16 weeks. The curriculum covers essential skills in Python, SQL, and statistics, focusing on creating predictive models and exploring machine learning algorithms such as Decision Trees and Close Neighbors. Participants engage in hands-on projects that encompass the entire AI lifecycle, from development to deployment.

Classes are conducted three times a week with a maximum of 12 students, and the course is available in both English and Spanish. A recognized certificate is awarded upon completion.

